column2: The Darkside Detective Part 1 - Malice In Wonderland
column7:
The Darkside Detective, is a quirky, silly, and tremendously fun point-and-click adventure game from Spooky Doorway. The game follows six cases of Detective Francis McQueen, and his sidekick Officer Dooley, as they attempt to solve mysteries paranormal, strange, spooky, or just downright silly!

---------------------------------------------

The Darkside Detective is best viewed from the playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL1Be_cMfHOEdcnv9w-SB7zbZ8T6NS8X2j
